Yeah this is something riot never touched on. What do you do when youre trying to survive a camp? Honestly i dont even try to ward anymore simply because of how tedious and pointless it is (as soon as he comes into your lane you will lose your ward and be easily ganked anyway then proceed to wait another 5 minutes for a 150 second ward).

2 rules for posting on this forum. Id rather not have riot posting: They will likely say something along the lines of &quot;well you need to complete 3 impossible task 1 is milking the angriest bull in the known world 2 is getting the golden fleece from what i assume is a purple hydra and 3 is getting a decent amount of ward coverage with the current state of wards.&quot; They will probably simplyfy it tho "use cc."
{{champion:20}} {{champion:28}} {{champion:33}} {{champion:114}} 
Id also rather not have higher elos tip because they are almost guaranteed to say something along the lines of &quot;ask your jungler for a gank&quot; or &quot;plant the wards better&quot; as if were all gods at the game. Also since they will be extremely biased as they never admit that their teams are shit sometimes then proceed to go passive agressive as hell on stream. However if they do have a tip that isnt along those lines go ahead. 
{{champion:432}} {{champion:223}} {{champion:67}} {{champion:238}} 
The reason id rather have lower elos is simply because meanwhile it might not be the strongest of sources it will definitly help on the task of climbing in this elo. It will also come from experience in this elo.

Note if i sound angry in this note i apologize as the last time i won a ranked game i was 19/9/18. and before that it was 15/5. A little tilted right now. Im too tired to think of a closeing &quot;good luck in soloque and have a wonderful day.&quot;
